<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-03-15 01:45 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7187 &Cx1f; tth-z
u s BC-BBA-THIEL-COLUMN-SPI &LR;      03-15 0947
