<P>
   CHINA-U.S.-TRADE (Washington) _ Raw fur skins of mink, whole,
with or without head, tail or paws. Monolithic digital integrated
circuits obtained by MOS technology. These are the substance of
diplomatic progress between world superpowers. These days, when the
United States and China take confidence-building measures, they
deal in provisionally preserved capers, not submarine-based
missiles. By Joseph Kahn.
</P>
