<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-03-15 13:07 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7518 &Cx1f; tab-z
r k BC-HOT-TEXAS-ART-ECONOMI     03-15 1160
