to include a studio portrait of two young women in white gowns and
flowing veils. By Eileen McNamara.
</P>
<P>
   NYHAN-COLUMN (Undated) -- A tip of the cap to a selection of
books about the Irish. By David Nyhan.
</P>
<P>
   JACKSON-COLUMN (Undated) _ Simmons journalism students know why
John McCain did so well. By Derrick Jackson.
</P>
