workouts is a great equalizer in a fitness world where personal
trainers have traditionally been an option only for the affluent.
By Dick Lehr. 1200 words.
</P>
<P>
   BEAM-COLUMN (Undated) _ ``My day with Kozmo.'' A diary of a day
of orders from Kozmo.com, an instant gratification service for
college kids and the urban webocracy. By Alex Beam.
</P>
