</P>
<P>
   HKN-BRUINS-SWEENEY (Boston) _ In a nine-day period marked by the
departure of icon Ray Bourque and veteran wing Rob DiMaio, it
wasn't a shock that the Bruins held onto one of their few veterans
who has played his entire 12-year NHL career in Boston. By Nancy
Marrapese-Burrell. 800 words.
</P>
