   WOMEN-MAGAZINES (Undated) _ March is a big month for women's
sports, and a good time to find out whether women's sports
magazines will finally take off. By Gregg Krupa. 1065 words.
</P>
<P>
   SOC-REVOLUTION (Foxborough, Mass.) _ Despite the stability
provided by strong local ownership, persistent fan interest and
MLS's foundation, the Revolution's prospects are nearly as
mysterious as they were at the beginning. By Frank Dell'Apa. 845
words.
</P>
