Click on the Seasonal Pages link to find the page. A name and
password are required; if you don't have them, please call
syndicate sales manager Bob Farnell at 800-535-4425.
</P>
<P>
   Each page has a $20 download charge. New customers get the first
10 downloads free.
</P>
