   COXNET LIFESTYLES
</P>
<P>
   Art includes 27 color photos.
</P>
<P>
   OSCAR BALLOT PAGE -- A ballot for this year's Academy Awards
telecast. Includes a check-off box for nominees from the major
categories. Art includes color photos of actors and actresses in
the Best Actor, Best actress, Best Supporting Actor, Best
Supporting Actress and Best picture categories. Art also includes a
2-column photo of the Oscar statue.
</P>
<P>
   WITH: NOMINEES' PREVIOUS PERFORMANCES -- While you can't see the
Oscar-nominated performances yet on video, it's a perfect time to
look back at some of the nominees' earlier performances that helped
get them where they are today. (Uhler, Austin American-Statesman)
