<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 
 This ``separate buy'' article is from Latin Trade magazine,
America's leading journal of Latin American business, finance and
trade: &HT;    ALL TIED UP. Mexico's Pineda Covalin Design House is hitting it
big with a line of ties and scarves with pre-Hispanic motifs.
 &HT;    Filed as BC-FASHION:PREHISPANIC-TOUCH-LATINTRADE-NYTSF in ``f''
financial and ``l'' lifestyle.
 &HT;    
 (To publish this article, it must be purchased _ the rate is not
