<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    INTERNET NOT SERVING POOR, LOW-LITERACY AMERICANS, STUDY FINDS
 &HT;    410&AMP;add. Moving in (w) Washington and (f) financial categories.
