by matching up private investors with minorities who want to start
businesses. The national networking session will be in Atlanta the
second weekend in April. The Access to Capital Symposium and
Millionaire's Ball will be held April 7 and 8 at the Ritz Carlton
in downtown Atlanta. (Joyner, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 15.
