<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-03-15 18:33 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7920 &Cx1f; taf-z
u l BC-HOME-IMPROVEMENT-ART-     03-15 0816
