   BUSH-FUNDRAISING (Washington) _ Gov. George W. Bush and the GOP
gear up their money machines to pay for advertising and other
efforts to wage a vigorous pre-convention campaign against the
Democrats. The Bush campaign plans a dozen major fund-raising
