<SLUG> BC-BUSH16-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Bush on `next phase' of campaign
 &HT;    By Ken Herman
 &HT;    c. 2000 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
