Schreiber High School achieved a stunning victory in the nationwide
Intel Science Talent Search this year, producing the first-place
winner and two other finalists and stealing the thunder of the
highly selective New York City schools that have traditionally
dominated the contest. Viviana Risca, a Romanian immigrant who won
